chrome.notes: Implemented as X-Webkit-CSP header in Chrome 14.

firefox.notes: Implemented as X-Content-Security-Policy header in Firefox 4.

ie.notes: Implemented as X-Content-Security-Policy header, only supporting 'sandbox' directive.

safari.notes: Implemented as X-Webkit-CSP header in Safari 6.

safari_ios.notes: Implemented as X-Webkit-CSP header in iOS 5.1.

firefox.notes: Prior to Firefox 50, ping attributes of <a> elements weren't covered by connect-src.
